            {
              "title": "(2)",
              "content": "세부사항"
            },
            {
              "title": "①",
              "content": "Home Ventilator care 중인 환자"
            },
            {
              "title": "②",
              "content": "지속적 약물투여 환자: Inotropics, Antiarrythmics, Vasodilators, Thrombolytics, Sedatives, Uterine relaxants 등"
